<paragraph blockId="118.[151,1437,1039,2036]" pageId="118" pageNumber="119">
Since the holotype of 
<taxonomicName authority="Viette, 1949" authorityName="Viette" authorityYear="1949" box="[446,941,1220,1244]" class="Insecta" family="Gracillariidae" genus="Lithocolletis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="118" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariensis">
<emphasis box="[446,795,1220,1244]" italics="true" pageId="118" pageNumber="119">Lithocolletis madagascariensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Viette" box="[804,941,1220,1244]" firstAuthor="Viette" pageId="118" pageNumber="119" pagination="171 - 176" refId="ref201646" refString="Viette, P. (1949) Description de trois Microlepidopteres malgaches. Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar, Ser. A, 3 (2), 171 - 176." type="journal article" year="1949">Viette, 1949</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
